selector_to_html = {"a[href=\"joint_control.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1.6 </span>Joint Control<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p><strong>The joint control interfaces provide precise control over each robot joint, supporting multiple control modes and joint groups.</strong></p>", "a[href=\"preset_motion.html#id4\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Safety Notes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id4\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html#id5\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Arbitration Workflow<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id5\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><h3>Arbitration Mechanism<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id6\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><p><strong>Input Source Arbitration and Management Rules:</strong></p>", "a[href=\"modeswitch.html#id2\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Core Functions<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>Supports switching into the following basic motion modes:</p>", "a[href=\"modeswitch.html#id3\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Motion Mode Query Service<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html#id8\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Programming Examples<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id8\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>For detailed programming examples and code explanations, refer to:</p>", "a[href=\"#id1\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1 </span>Control Module<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p><strong>AgiBot X2 AimDK Control Module \u2013 Providing a Complete Low-Level Robot Control Interface</strong></p><p>The control module is a core component of the AgiBot X2 AimDK, providing comprehensive low-level control interfaces for the robot. It follows the ROS2 standard and supports both C++ and Python, enabling developers to achieve flexible and efficient robot control.</p>", "a[href=\"locomotion.html#id2\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Control Functions<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"joint_control.html#id6\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Joint State Query Service<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id6\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"joint_control.html#id5\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Joint Control Topics<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id5\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>Joints are controlled by body part (arms, legs, waist, head), and closed-loop control can be implemented using status feedback.</p>", "a[href=\"locomotion.html#id3\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Locomotion Control Topic<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"modeswitch.html#id4\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Motion Mode Set Service<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id4\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"modeswitch.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1.1 </span>Motion Mode Switching<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p><strong>The mode-switch and locomotion interfaces provide core capabilities for switching motion modes and controlling walking/running.</strong></p>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html#id7\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Safety Notes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id7\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"locomotion.html#id4\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Programming Examples<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id4\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>For detailed programming examples and code explanations, refer to:</p>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html#id1\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Key Features<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><h3>Multi-Source Integration<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#mc-input-source-list\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3>", "a[href=\"locomotion.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1.2 </span>Locomotion Control<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p><strong>The locomotion control interfaces provide the core functions for controlling the robot\u2019s walking and running velocities.</strong></p>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html#id2\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Hand Control Features<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"joint_control.html#id8\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Safety Notes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id8\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html#id3\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Hand Control Topics<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"modeswitch.html#id6\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Safety Notes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id6\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"modeswitch.html#id5\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Programming Examples<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id5\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>For detailed programming examples and code explanations, see:</p>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html#id4\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Hand Status Topics<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id4\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1.5 </span>End Effector Control<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p>The end-effector control module currently supports:</p>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html#id7\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Input Source Management Services<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id7\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"locomotion.html#id5\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Safety Notes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id5\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html#id3\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Input Source Configuration<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><h3>Priority Reference<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id4\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html#id9\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Notes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id9\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"MC_control.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1.3 </span>MC Control Signal Configuration<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#mc\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p><strong>MC control signal configuration provides unified management of multiple input sources, ensuring the robot always responds to the highest-priority control signal.</strong></p><p>Control signal configuration is one of the core features of the AgiBot X2 AimDK, enabling unified management and priority arbitration among multiple control sources. This mechanism ensures that when multiple control inputs are active, the robot safely and reliably responds to the command with the highest priority.</p>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html#id5\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Hand Type Query Service<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id5\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"endeffector.html#id6\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Programming Examples<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id6\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>For detailed programming examples and explanations, refer to:</p>", "a[href=\"joint_control.html#id7\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Programming Examples<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id7\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>For detailed examples and code explanations, refer to:</p>", "a[href=\"preset_motion.html#id2\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Preset Motion Control Service<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>", "a[href=\"joint_control.html#id2\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Key Features<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><h3>Control Modes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3>", "a[href=\"preset_motion.html#id3\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Programming Examples<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><p>For detailed programming examples and code explanations, see:</p>", "a[href=\"preset_motion.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\"><span class=\"section-number\">5.1.4 </span>Preset Motion Control<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><p><strong>Preset motion control allows the robot to execute predefined actions such as waving, handshaking, raising an arm, etc. With a simple service call, the robot can quickly perform specific actions, making this interface ideal for common interaction scenarios.</strong></p>"}
